ğŸ“ Drone Security Lab Syllabus (12 Weeks)

Week 1: UAS threat models & ethics
Week 2: PX4 & ArduPilot architectures
Week 3: Firmware build & integrity
Week 4: Secure boot & signing
Week 5: MAVLink protocol security
Week 6: Telemetry logging & anomaly detection
Week 7: GNSS resilience & failsafes
Week 8: Sensor fusion attacks & mitigation
Week 9: Vision-based navigation fallback
Week 10: Supply-chain risks
Week 11: Incident response simulation
Week 12: Final resilience assessment


