ğŸ”’ CI Guardrails (Recommended)

To keep the repository clean and legal:

Require PR templates with legality checkboxes

Block keywords related to jamming or interference

Require citations for research claims

Enforce documentation-only contributions


Example CI checks:

Markdown linting

Link validation

Keyword scanning



